sentences: He was born Takushi Yamazaki (山崎卓志, Yamazaki Takushi) on November 16, 1966, in Miyazu, Kyoto, Japan.
Masonna (マゾンナ) was started in 1987 in Osaka as Maso Yamazaki's noise project.
In 2018, Maso began performing and releasing under the name Controlled Death.
In 1996 Masonna toured the United States on the "American Mystique Tour" named after his album Inner Mind Mystique.
